  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. Factual stub. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A self-hosted deployment daemon: push to GitHub and your code deploys to a Docker VPS automatically — push-to-deploy without a CI platform. Auto-detects project type and deployment strategy, and reports status back to GitHub and Discord. Comes with a dashboard for watching deployments, projects, and logs.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The dockrune dashboard — push-to-deploy, smart detection, and real-time status\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/dockrune/dashboard.png\" alt=\"The dockrune dashboard — push-to-deploy, smart detection, and real-time status\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/dockrune/dashboard.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/dockrune/dashboard.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/dockrune/dashboard.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/dockrune/dashboard.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The dockrune dashboard — push-to-deploy, smart detection, and real-time status\" width=\"1440\" height=\"947\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.88deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1440×947\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The dockrune dashboard — push-to-deploy, smart detection, and real-time status</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The deploy worker — queued deployments processed in Go\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/dockrune/code.png\" alt=\"The deploy worker — queued deployments processed in Go\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/dockrune/code.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/dockrune/code.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/dockrune/code.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/dockrune/code.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The deploy worker — queued deployments processed in Go\" width=\"1400\" height=\"980\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.92deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1400×980\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The deploy worker — queued deployments processed in Go</figcaption>\n</figure>",
